doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='')
        meta(name='author', content='')

        title Football

        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/img/favicon.ico')

        // Font Awesome icons (free version)
        script(src='https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.3/js/all.js', crossorigin='anonymous')

        // Google fonts
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Varela+Round', rel='stylesheet')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Nunito:200,200i,300,300i,400,400i,600,600i,700,700i,800,800i,900,900i', rel='stylesheet')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body#page-top

        // Navigation
        nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-light.fixed-top
            .container
                a.navbar-brand.js-scroll-trigger(href='#page-top') Home
                button.navbar-toggler.navbar-toggler-right(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    | Menu
                    i.fas.fa-bars
                #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.ml-auto
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.js-scroll-trigger(href='#about') About
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.js-scroll-trigger(href='#projects') History
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.js-scroll-trigger(href='#signup') Contact

        // Masthead
        header.masthead
            .container.d-flex.h-100.align-items-center
                .mx-auto.text-center
                    h1.mx-auto.my-0.text-uppercase Football
                    h2.text-white-50.mx-auto.mt-2.mb-5 Welcome to our website! Here you can start our quiz or continue with the general pieces of information about Football
                    a.btn.btn-primary.js-scroll-trigger(href='#about') About
                    a.btn.btn-primary.js-scroll-trigger(href='http://localhost:4000') Quiz

        // About
        section#about.about-section.text-center
            .container
                .row
                    .col-lg-8.mx-auto
                        h2.text-white.mb-4 What is football in general?
                        p.text-white-50
                            | Football is the kind of sport where 22 players go on the pitch and trying to score a goal, and the team who scores the most goals wins
                img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/ipad.png', alt='...')

        // History
        section#projects.projects-section.bg-light
            .container
                // Featured Project Row
                .row
                        .col-lg-8.mx-auto
                            h4.text.black.mb-4 History
                            p.text-black-50
                                | Records trace the history of soccer back more than 2,000 years ago to ancient China. Greece, Rome, and parts of Central America also claim to have started the sport; but it was England that transitioned soccer, or what the British and many other people around the world call “football,” into the game we know today.
                        img.img-fluid.mb-7(src='assets/img/old-picture.png', alt='...')
                // Project One Row
                .row.justify-content-center.no-gutters.mb-5.mb-lg-0
                    .col-lg-6
                        img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/demo-image-01.jpg', alt='...')
                    .col-lg-6
                        .bg-black.text-center.h-100.project
                            .d-flex.h-100
                                .project-text.w-100.my-auto.text-center.text-lg-left
                                    h4.text-white Misty
                                    p.mb-0.text-white-50
                                        | Every country has its own league where different teams play against each other and the best Teams may participate in the champions legaue or in the europa legaue (only europe teams). but the best in their own league do not always come to these tournaments sometimes only the first, second, third or fourth come to these tournaments or have to play qualifying games for the tournaments
                                    hr.d-none.d-lg-block.mb-0.ml-0
                // Project Two Row
                .row.justify-content-center.no-gutters
                    .col-lg-6
                        img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/demo-image-02.jpg', alt='...')
                    .col-lg-6.order-lg-first
                        .bg-black.text-center.h-100.project
                            .d-flex.h-100
                                .project-text.w-100.my-auto.text-center.text-lg-right
                                    h4.text-white Mountains
                                    p.mb-0.text-white-50
                                        | Another example of a project with its respective description. These sections work well responsively as well, try this theme on a small screen!
                                    hr.d-none.d-lg-block.mb-0.mr-0

        // Signup
        section#signup.signup-section
            .container
                .row
                    .col-md-10.col-lg-8.mx-auto.text-center
                        i.far.fa-paper-plane.fa-2x.mb-2.text-white
                        h2.text-white.mb-5 Subscribe to receive updates!
                        form.form-inline.d-flex
                            input#inputEmail.form-control.flex-fill.mr-0.mr-sm-2.mb-3.mb-sm-0(type='email', placeholder='Enter email address...')
                            button.btn.btn-primary.mx-auto(type='submit') Subscribe

        // Contact
        section.contact-section.bg-black
            .container
                .row
                    .col-md-4.mb-3.mb-md-0
                        .card.py-4.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center
                                i.fas.fa-map-marked-alt.text-primary.mb-2
                                h4.text-uppercase.m-0 Address
                                hr.my-4
                                .small.text-black-50 Limesstraße 12- 14 · 4060 Leonding
                    .col-md-4.mb-3.mb-md-0
                        .card.py-4.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center
                                i.fas.fa-envelope.text-primary.mb-2
                                h4.text-uppercase.m-0 Email
                                hr.my-4
                                .small.text-black-50
                                    a(href='mailto:berdankadir12@gmail.com') berdankadir12@gmail.com
                    .col-md-4.mb-3.mb-md-0
                        .card.py-4.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center
                                i.fas.fa-mobile-alt.text-primary.mb-2
                                h4.text-uppercase.m-0 Phone
                                hr.my-4
                                .small.text-black-50 +43 732 6733680
                .social.d-flex.justify-content-center
                    a.mx-2(href='https://twitter.com/karlof002')
                        i.fab.fa-twitter
                    a.mx-2(href='https://www.facebook.com/ExynoOffical')
                        i.fab.fa-facebook-f
                    a.mx-2(href='https://github.com/karlof002/football')
                        i.fab.fa-github

        // Footer
        footer.footer.bg-black.small.text-center.text-white-50
            .container
                | Copyright &copy; Football-Website 2021

        // Bootstrap core JS
        script(src='https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js')
        script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')

        // Third party plugin JS
        script(src='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animejs/3.2.1/anime.min.js')

        // Core theme JS
        script(src='js/scripts.js')
